FYI before you lose your mind trying a hundred different corsair icue keyboard profiles, 99% of them do not work with the Y740 keyboard since it's not supported for all the corsair features like actions keys for example. 

You can make your own of course and there's a handful on the community site but the vast majority of them are not compatible.

https://alexkrastev.herokuapp.com/profiles/corsair/community_profiles?utf8=%E2%9C%93&search=&devices_filter%5B%5D=28&sort_option=newest&brand=Corsair
